      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTORMZABREWEN (4) was responsible for a very good effort last time over 1680m at this track, finishing second and just 1.3 metres from the winner. Big chance based on that recent effort. FANCY ANOTHER (6) had put together a string of strong performances then added to the list last start when she finished second over 2200m at this track, beaten 2.75 metres. That latest effort is good enough to take out a race like this. CHARLI PIPPEN (10) is at the track for the first time. By Fear The Dragon and hails from the R P Gillie stable. Draws out a little on the second line and may need luck at some point. Placed in a recent trial. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to his career. ULTIMATE ATOM (2) is a four-year-old mare by Ultimate Machete from Shes An Atom on debut. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Showed some ability when a minor placegetter in a recent trial. Will be right there at the business end.",
